		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Could there be some manditory time delay between register writes for them to have effect?  Kind of like how the MMC3 needs to have 9 or so PPU cycles between A12 rising edges for the counter to decrement... maybe MMC1 needs at least 2 CPU cycles between register writes?

		

